OL,3,CWoman dies after falling from car in
OL,4,CKent
OL,6,FPolice are appealing for witnesses and
OL,7,Fdashcam footage after a woman in her
OL,8,F80s died following a crash in
OL,9,FTonbridge.
OL,11,FThe incident happened on Hectorage
OL,12,FRoad at around 5.30pm on Tuesday 3
OL,13,FMarch.
OL,15,FAs a stationary silver Vauxhall Mokka
OL,16,Fmoved off, the rear nearside passenger
OL,17,Ffell from the vehicle onto the road.
OL,19,FThe passenger, a woman in her 80s,
OL,20,Fsuffered critical injuries and went to
OL,21,Fhospital where she later died.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/2
